<table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=10>
<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="mystic_cloak"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Mystic Cloak - AC 8</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/back.shtml">Back</a><BR>
Weight: 0.5 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/enchanter/armour/back.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/back.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/back.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/back.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/steelskin.shtml?spellID=91">Steelskin</a><BR>
Charges: 10<BR>
<font color=red>
(No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +5) (Sv Magic +5) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/mystic_cloak.shtml?questID=44">Mystic Cloak</a> quest<BR>

</td></tr>
