<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Machput</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-22 07:42:11</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>i am a lv35 human necro and just completed this quest<BR>
<BR>
you can do it with dubiosly faction standing but get a bad<BR>
faction hit on The Dead<BR>
<BR>
to do this quest u gotta kill the priest of Najena in Unrest<BR>
(spawn +500, +50 inside the house) and he is a rare spawn and<BR>
there is a spawn rate of 55mins on his spot<BR>
<BR>
then head to Najena and look for a high elf prisoner and talk to<BR>
her<BR>
<BR>
give her the key and head to felwith with the note you get from her<BR>
<BR>
find her father (same surname) near the water<BR>
<BR>
give him the note and head with the cloak you get to erudin<BR>
and find again another highelf wich is the mother of the<BR>
prisoner<BR>
<BR>
you will find her on second floor in ENC guild and give her the<BR>
cloak <BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
