<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just a side note to all you Necros out there. Besides having faction to get into a city, I have been told by a friend in and out of the game that you can be invis and give someone an item and remain invis while and after you give the NPC an item. So if your faction has nothing to do with the quest, hence you have to have good faction to even get the quest, any Necro should be able to do this quest.</font></td></tr></table>
